    "headline": "LMS Compliance & Certifications: The Complete Guide for 2026",
    "description": "A comprehensive guide to LMS compliance features including SCORM, xAPI, SOC 2, GDPR, certificate management, accreditation support, and regulatory training requirements across major learning platforms.",
